Package: orthologr
Type: Package
Title: A package combining common gene orthology detection methods and dN/dS
    models for pipeline processing.
Version: 0.0.1
Date: 2014-06-08
Author: Hajk-Georg Drost, Sarah Scharfenberg, Kristian Karsten Ullrich
Maintainer: Hajk-Georg Drost <hajk-georg.drost@informatik.uni-halle.de>
Description: The present collection of functions can be used to perform
    orthology detection and dN/dS computations for biological research.
License: GPL-3
Depends:
    R (>= 3.1.1)
Imports:
    seqinr (>= 3.0-7),
    data.table (>= 1.9.4),
    parallel (>= 3.0.2),
    dplyr (>= 0.3.0.2),
    doMC (>= 1.3.3),
    foreach (>= 1.4.2),
    Rcpp (>= 0.11.3),
    Biostrings (>= 2.32.1),
    RSQLite (>= 0.11.4),
    stringr (>= 0.6.2)
LinkingTo: Rcpp
